# Core Modularity Rules

Every feature must:

- Live in its own kebab-case folder
- Components must use PascalCase prefix matching folder
- Shared logic must live in `use*.ts`
- Optional `config.ts` for definitions

Example:
activities-history-list/
  ActivitiesHistoryList.vue
  ActivitiesHistoryListTable.vue
  useActivitiesTable.ts
  config.ts